Breaking change: Native tuples now create `TupleConfig` values instead of `ListConfig` values, and conversion returns native tuples instead of lists. Code that expects tuple-derived configs to be `ListConfig`, checks `OmegaConf.is_list()`, or expects converted values to be `list` must be updated. See [Migrating tuple usage in OmegaConf 2.4](https://omegaconf.readthedocs.io/en/latest/tuple_migration.html).
